AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002413> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ro/docs/causal-relations>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002413> "provides input for"@en)
SubObjectPropertyOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002413> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002412>)
SubObjectPropertyOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002413> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002414>)

